OL,3,CSchoolboy waited for pupils to sleep
OL,4,Cbefore alleged hammer attack, court
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FA public schoolboy was "on a mission"
OL,8,Fto protect himself from a zombie
OL,9,Fapocalypse when he attacked two
OL,10,Fsleeping students and a teacher with
OL,11,Fhammers at a boarding school, a court
OL,12,Fhas heard.
OL,14,FThe 16-year-old was wearing just his
OL,15,Fboxer shorts and claimed he was
OL,16,Fsleepwalking when he attacked the two
OL,17,Fboys and the housemaster at Blundell's
OL,18,FSchool in Tiverton, Devon.
