OL,3,CSchoolboy waited for pupils to sleep
OL,4,Cbefore alleged hammer attack, court
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FExeter Crown Court heard the teenager,
OL,8,Fwho cannot be identified for legal
OL,9,Freasons, had armed himself with three
OL,10,Fclaw hammers and waited for the two
OL,11,Fboys to be asleep before allegedly
OL,12,Fattacking them.
OL,14,FJames Dawes KC, prosecuting, said the
OL,15,Ftwo boys were asleep in cabin-style
OL,16,Fbeds in one of the co-ed school's
OL,17,Fboarding houses when the defendant
OL,18,Fclimbed up and attacked them shortly
OL,19,Fbefore 1am on 9 June last year.
