OL,3,CSchoolboy waited for pupils to sleep
OL,4,Cbefore alleged hammer attack, court
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,F"He had four of them and he selected
OL,8,Fmore than one hammer and he quietly
OL,9,Fclimbed up into the top of the first
OL,10,Fcabin bed.
OL,12,F"The boys are asleep, and they had
OL,13,Fboth had their heads on pillows, and
OL,14,Fthen he smashed a hammer or hammers
OL,15,Finto their heads as they slept,
OL,16,Fmultiple times.
