OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,F"He also hit arms and backs. He didn't
OL,8,Fjust use the flat end of the hammer `
OL,9,Fhe used the claw end as well to strike
OL,10,Fthese boys. These blows smashed their
OL,11,Fskulls."
OL,13,FThe court heard housemaster Henry
OL,14,FRoffe-Silvester, who was asleep in his
OL,15,Fown quarters, was awoken by noises
OL,16,Fcoming from the boarding house and
OL,17,Fwent to investigate.
