OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FWhen he entered the bedroom where the
OL,8,Falleged attack happened, he saw a
OL,9,Fsilhouetted figure standing in the
OL,10,Froom who turned towards him and
OL,11,Frepeatedly struck him over the head
OL,12,Fwith a hammer.
OL,14,FAnother student heard Mr Roffe-
OL,15,FSilvester's shouts and swearing as he
OL,16,Ffled the bedroom and dialled 999 `
OL,17,Fbelieving there was an intruder.
