OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,F"Mr Roffe-Silvester retreated down the
OL,8,Fcorridor, with the defendant attacking
OL,9,Fhim again and again with the hammer
OL,10,Faround his face and head," Mr Dawes
OL,11,Fsaid.
OL,13,F"He was shouting at the defendant to
OL,14,Fstop. In total there were six impacts
OL,15,Fto his head.
OL,17,F"He said the defendant was
OL,18,Fexpressionless, he was neutral and
OL,19,Funsettling in his expression and
OL,20,Fappearance.
