OL,3,CSchoolboy waited for pupils to sleep
OL,4,Cbefore alleged hammer attack, court
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,F"The defendant told the student he had
OL,8,Fhammers and he had been watching
OL,9,Fhorror movies lately and he had them
OL,10,Fto protect himself."
OL,12,FMr Dawes said the defendant told the
OL,13,Fstudent he had fallen asleep after
OL,14,Fwatching a movie and then carried out
OL,15,Fthe attack.
OL,17,FThe prosecutor suggested this was a
OL,18,Flie because there was evidence the boy
OL,19,Fhad been using his iPad until moments
OL,20,Fbefore the alleged assaults.
