OL,3,CSchoolboy waited for pupils to sleep
OL,4,Cbefore alleged hammer attack, court
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,F"The student tried to calm the
OL,8,Fdefendant down and asked him again
OL,9,Fwhat had happened, and the defendant
OL,10,Fsaid to the student he was watching
OL,11,Fhorror movies and he had weapons to
OL,12,Fprepare for the zombie apocalypse and
OL,13,Fto protect himself," Mr Dawes said.
OL,15,FOne student heard the defendant say:
OL,16,F"I am sorry, I was dreaming."
OL,18,FAnd another told police the teenager
OL,19,Fsaid: "I am going to prison, I was
OL,20,Fsleepwalking."
