OL,3,CSchoolboy waited for pupils to sleep
OL,4,Cbefore alleged hammer attack, court
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,F"You may think that whoever does that
OL,8,Fintends to kill the person they are
OL,9,Fattacking. They were sleeping at the
OL,10,Ftime and astonishingly they both
OL,11,Fsurvived these attacks.
OL,13,F"Their survival has nothing to do with
OL,14,Fthe defendant and his actions but
OL,15,Feverything to do with the speed at
OL,16,Fwhich the 999 call was made by a boy
OL,17,Fat school and the astonishing skill of
OL,18,Fthe paramedics who arrived and the
OL,19,Fskilful work of the doctors and
OL,20,Fsurgeons who saved their lives at the
OL,21,Fhospital."
